<refsect1 role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
SexyTreeView is a GtkTreeView which supports tooltips on individual cells.
These tooltips can be either text (stored in a column of the tree model) or
widgets, created through a signal handler.
</para>
</refsect1>

